--- Five Nights at Freddy's made using JavaScript, HTML5 and CSS by streetz ---
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

FNaF JS is a small project I'm working on which recreates the original FNaF 1 with some additional gameplay changes made.

Trello where you can see the progress made on the project so far: https://trello.com/b/3maV07eF/fnaf-java-script

------------------------
--- Gameplay changes ---
------------------------

- Added a mechanic from UCN where you can toggle the desk fan which will cool down your office but will waste power. If you don't have the fan on at all you will being to see less

- Reduced the camera size

- Added a secondary tablet which shows all the statistics

- Changed the behaviour of Foxy and Golden Freddy 😁👍👍👍
